[index.html](mdc:index.html)

When updating the homepage with content, follow these guidelines:

- **Title + Description SEO**: Update the `<title>`, `<meta name="description">`, and `<meta name="keywords">` tags in the `<head>` to match the provided brand, description, and keywords. Keywords should be generated based on the title and description if not explicitly provided.
- **Schema**: Replace or update the `<script type="application/ld+json">` block with the provided JSON-LD schema, ensuring it matches the current brand, address, menu, cuisine, and hours.
- **Brand Name**: Update all visible brand name text (e.g., in the navbar) to the new brand.
- **Our Story**: Update the "Our Story" section content to reflect the new brand's story, if provided.

**Important:** Only change the content as specified. Do not alter the HTML structure, CSS, or JavaScript. Preserve all layout and style.